    "description": "MONSTER CRUSH C4 DEMOLITION EDITION is the long awaited HD remake from the IOS hit game.<br />\r\nThis version was build for PC from the ground up, with new and improved graphics and includes all the bonus levels and materials! <br />\r\nMonster Crush is a physics based puzzle game that puts you in the role of a demolition expert.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlien Monsters have invaded the planet. Our weapons are useless.<br />\r\nThere is only one way of stopping them: Crush them with our skyscrapers!<br />\r\nPlant your bombs in the tallest buildings and watch them fall on the invaders.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n7 cities to liberate<br />\r\n42 unique puzzle levels<br />\r\n20000+ user contributed levels<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2 types of bombs:<br />\r\n1- The Black Bomb: Makes a nice round hole in a building but can only destroy soft materials like bricks and concrete.<br />\r\n2- The Cutter: Slices a piece off the building. Can cut through heavy steel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMultiple puzzle game modes:<br />\r\n1- Bowling: Get a wrecking ball as far as possible.<br />\r\n2- Crush Monsters: Try to crush all monsters.<br />\r\n3- Girder Construction: Make constructions to guide the wrecking ball.<br />\r\n4- Demolition: Blow as much up as possible using high explosives.<br />\r\n5- Limbo Dancing: Get the building below a certain level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game uses advanced physics to simulate the destruction.<br />\r\nGames like &quot;Angry Birds&quot; and &quot;Implode&quot; use only stacked boxes. <br />\r\nNow whole buildings can collapse to the ground.<br />\r\nWindows will break and dust will fill the sky!",
